{"tid":2253550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航空業從此之後短程不設空少空姐只設安全督導員有冇得諗?","createTime":"2020-10-22T08:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T12:35:39.000Z","uid":70429,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6019141e024f471571af04373c7149c1ec73e019","tid":2253550,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"講真,飛機入面,空姐空少既所謂service係真係捆綁式消費來.<br />\n<br />\n去短程如台灣or日本, 1-3hrs, 我可能連水都唔需要問佢地拎, 落機已經秒唔記得佢地個樣,<br />\n<br />\n中間同佢地幾乎0接觸但係又要養埋佢地, 張貴到癡線既正價機票入面當中有幾多劃落佢地份糧度我唔知啦. 但佢地個定位其實又唔係必然需要, 例如檢查安全帶, 其實搵1~2個安全督導員(約萬5月薪同保安同價)既職位, 只負責督導性執法, 見到你冇綁安全帶就提你, 但唔會幫你遞行李.<br />\n<br />\n從此之後中短程就永遠cut曬多餘空姐空少,有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"67fbcbfde44cbcb53ea43e5931b2ad171591a6d3","tid":2253550,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"UO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba427801a88c04b74a1346d7481bf0cf2d8a7d6","tid":2253550,"uid":42487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"就算cut左人手 你既機票價錢都唔會變 係航空公司賺多左"},{"pid":"679f6b8485e817688d397d79a6a724cc95d75d3f","tid":2253550,"uid":161374,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"用香港警察咪得，邊個有投訴就打"},{"pid":"f2b155a960ca227224a30699e67eb02f4650ec7f","tid":2253550,"uid":294648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:02.000Z","msg":"飛機上唔可以缺少專業人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f924bc7d0881a8df427c7b5f039cabfb002793b","tid":2253550,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"換酒樓呀姐上去"},{"pid":"acaa011565e12ca86f97c2e4731d8f768e316766","tid":2253550,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"on9 post 拉喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"